---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="BeamCash Demo - SkanPay"
  description="See how BeamCash demonstrates the QR checkout workflow SkanPay wants merchants, payment partners, and future financial partners to understand."
  activePath="/beamcash-demo/"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">BeamCash demo</p>
    <h1>A simple walkthrough of QR checkout</h1>
    <p>
      BeamCash shows how a seller creates a QR code and how a buyer completes checkout.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section demo-intro">
    <div>
      <img class="beamcash-wordmark" src="/beamcash/beamcash-wordmark.svg" alt="BeamCash" />
      <p class="eyebrow">Why it is here</p>
      <h2>BeamCash demonstrates the experience. SkanPay is the gateway vision.</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        The demo helps merchants, banks, investors, and payment partners see the checkout flow before a deeper integration conversation.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="spec-panel">
      <div class="spec-row">
        <span>BeamCash</span>
        <p>Working MVP that shows the user experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-row">
        <span>SkanPay</span>
        <p>Patent-pending QR payment gateway model and partner opportunity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-row">
        <span>Boundary</span>
        <p>Demo only. This website does not process live payments or collect payment credentials.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Walkthrough</p>
        <h2>How the demo works</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        Follow the product flow from seller setup to buyer checkout.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="walkthrough">
      <article class="walkthrough-step flow-overview">
        <div>
          <span>Overview</span>
          <h3>Seller setup to checkout confirmation</h3>
          <p>BeamCash shows the full concept: seller setup, QR sign, buyer checkout, confirmation, and dashboard access.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/beamcash/beamcash-product-flow.svg" alt="BeamCash product flow from seller setup to QR sign, buyer checkout, confirmation, and dashboard" />
      </article>
      <article class="walkthrough-step">
        <div>
          <span>Step 1</span>
          <h3>Seller creates a QR code</h3>
          <p>The seller dashboard shows readiness status, payment activity, and the QR code customers can scan.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/beamcash/beamcash-seller-dashboard-mobile.png" alt="BeamCash seller dashboard with QR code and readiness status" />
      </article>
      <article class="walkthrough-step">
        <div>
          <span>Step 2</span>
          <h3>Buyer reviews and pays</h3>
          <p>The buyer sees the merchant profile, selects an amount, and proceeds through checkout.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/beamcash/beamcash-buyer-checkout-mobile.png" alt="BeamCash buyer checkout screen with merchant profile and payment amount" />
      </article>
      <article class="walkthrough-step">
        <div>
          <span>Step 3</span>
          <h3>Seller can recover the code</h3>
          <p>A returning seller can find an existing code instead of rebuilding the setup from scratch.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/beamcash/beamcash-find-code-mobile.png" alt="BeamCash recovery screen for finding a seller code" />
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Next step</p>
      <h2>Use the demo to guide the integration conversation.</h2>
      <p>Share the merchant, wallet, or partner flow you want to evaluate.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">Request a Demo</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
